Output demo.mp4
Set Width 1600
Set Height 1200

Set VideoCRF 8
Set VideoPreset slow
Set VideoBitrate 5000000

Set Shell zsh
Set TypingSpeed 75ms
Type "./bin/bewitch -config data/bewitch.toml"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Right
Sleep 2s
Right
Sleep 2s
Right
Sleep 2s
Right
Sleep 2s
Right
Sleep 2s
Right
Sleep 1.5s
Escape
PageDown
Sleep 250ms
PageDown
Sleep 250ms
PageDown
Sleep 2s
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
